 with &#8220;total blocking time&#8221; Images: add field to list images to be excluded [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"frank\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2763:\"<p><a href=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ao_28_defer_not_aggregate.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-11168\" src=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ao_28_defer_not_aggregate-300x210.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ao_28_defer_not_aggregate-300x210.jpg 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ao_28_defer_not_aggregate-624x437.jpg 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/ao_28_defer_not_aggregate.jpg 975w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>I&#8217;m sure you have been good this year so Santa cannot but put a nice ribbon around the next version of Autoptimize, out later this month. These are the most important changes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>JavaScript</strong>: new option &#8220;<strong>defer but don&#8217;t aggregate</strong>&#8221; which *might* help with &#8220;total blocking time&#8221;</li>\n<li><strong>Images</strong>: add field to list <strong>images to be excluded from image optimization</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Critical CSS</strong>: <strong>major improvements</strong> of the job <strong>processing</strong> mechanism, reducing time spent from up to 1 minute to <strong>just a couple of seconds</strong>.</li>\n<li>Critical CSS: under &#8220;advanced options&#8221; replace &#8220;request limit&#8221; with &#8220;queue processing time limit&#8221; (default 30s).</li>\n<li>Extra | Google Fonts: better parsing of version 2 Google Font URL&#8217;s (/css2/).</li>\n<li>Misc. other minor fixes, see <a href=\"https://github.com/futtta/autoptimize/commit\">the GitHub commit log</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>In case you want to give Santa a hand with all that wrapping up, you can always <a href=\"https://github.com/futtta/autoptimize/archive/beta.zip\">download the Beta version here</a> and take it out for a spin.</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/04/11/autoptimize-2-2-coming-your-way-care-to-test/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Autoptimize 2.2 coming your way, care to test?\">Autoptimize 2.2 coming your way, care to test? </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/03/04/want-to-test-automated-critical-css-creation/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Want to test automated Critical CSS creation?\">Want to test automated Critical CSS creation? </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/05/24/autoptimize-2-4-beta-3-includes-image-optimization/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Autoptimize 2.4 beta 3 includes image optimization!\">Autoptimize 2.4 beta 3 includes image optimization! </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_autoptimize/~4/8sVlkoxxekM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2020/12/07/santa-wrapping-up-autoptimize-2-8/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.o