\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:389:\"Some people asked for documentation/ information on that new autoptimize_filter_imgopt_lazyload_from_nth filter which allows one to tell AO not to optimize the first X images found in the HTML, so here is an example code snippet that sees AO not lazyload the first 5 images: add_filter( \'autoptimize_filter_imgopt_lazyload_from_nth\', function(){ return 5; } ); Update: as from AO [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"frank\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2053:\"<p><a href=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-11187\" src=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026-300x144.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"144\" srcset=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026-300x144.jpg 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026-1024x493.jpg 1024w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026-624x300.jpg 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Selection_999026.jpg 1203w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Some people asked for documentation/ information on that new autoptimize_filter_imgopt_lazyload_from_nth filter which allows one to tell AO not to optimize the first X images found in the HTML, so here is an example code snippet that sees AO not lazyload the first 5 images:</p>\n<p><code>add_filter( \'autoptimize_filter_imgopt_lazyload_from_nth\', function(){ return 5; } );</code></p>\n<p>Update: as from AO 2.8.2 this will also be an option on the settings page, see screenshot :)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2016/07/24/preparing-for-autoptimize-2-0-3-or-2-1-0/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Preparing (for) Autoptimize 2.0.3 or 2.1.0\">Preparing (for) Autoptimize 2.0.3 or 2.1.0 </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/08/11/loading-webfonts-just-for-a-title-switch-to-svg-instead/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Loading webfonts just for a title? Switch to SVG instead.\">Loading webfonts just for a title? Switch to SVG instead. </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/01/23/of-bugs-inconsistencies-and-tag-soup-in-future-core/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Of bugs, inconsistencies and tag soup in (future) core\">Of bugs, inconsistencies and tag soup in (future) core </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_wordpress/~4/2YjsEf-1qyw\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:117:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2020/12/11/about-that-new-autoptimize-autoptimize_filter_imgopt_lazyload_from_nth-filter/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"6\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:112:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2020/12/11/about-that-new-autoptimize-autoptimize_filter_imgopt_la